{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"author":"Miguel de Guzman","homeCity":"Philippines"}},"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/53b42969835fb73187827a9c4c1f0379/8af60/stevejobs.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 99.46619217081852%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"stevejobs\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/53b42969835fb73187827a9c4c1f0379/c739e/stevejobs.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/53b42969835fb73187827a9c4c1f0379/8ee9c/stevejobs.jpg 148w,\n/static/53b42969835fb73187827a9c4c1f0379/ebbe7/stevejobs.jpg 295w,\n/static/53b42969835fb73187827a9c4c1f0379/c739e/stevejobs.jpg 590w,\n/static/53b42969835fb73187827a9c4c1f0379/5413e/stevejobs.jpg 885w,\n/static/53b42969835fb73187827a9c4c1f0379/8af60/stevejobs.jpg 1124w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n     </p>\n<p><strong><em>Multidisciplinary, extreme design thinking and focus - Steve Jobs’s views are arguably about how we will use technology shaped the future and paved ways for people like me to create and express more..</em></strong></p>\n<p>A  big part of my life is my fascination with Steve Jobs ideas. Most of my professional practice as an accountant is some how predicated on ideas or concepts that revolved on curiousity which very much against the typical office working type mindset which you should just do what you are told, less time to accomplish it as much as possible. </p>\n<p>Steve imagined that tech should be interpreted to the normal person, much easier than remembering software concepts. The hardpart of software development I guess is it was created by people where they hardly haven’t made things in very structured ways, unlike other disciplines of development like engineering and architecture </p>","excerpt":"  Multidisciplinary, extreme design thinking and focus - Steve Jobs’s views are arguably about how we will use technology shaped the future…","fields":{"tagSlugs":["/tags/creating-art/","/tags/tech/","/tags/history/","/tags/blog/"]},"frontmatter":{"title":"Think Different","tags":["creating-art","tech","history","blog"],"date":"November 11, 2019"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/think-different/"}}